    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a vehicle that truly balances reliability with style! This car is in good condition, a clear testament to its consistent maintenance and the care it has received from its previous owner. It offers a smooth, dependable driving experience and looks great inside and out\u2014perfect for anyone seeking a high-quality, well-loved ride!",
      "price": 36800.0,
