    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. It starts up reliably and runs smoothly, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver or a family car. The interior is clean and shows only minimal signs of wear, while the exterior maintains a high-quality finish with no major blemishes. Prospective buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
